We are celebrating our 1 year anniversary this month and we have a deal for you. We just launched a new server in Buffalo, NY and have a fresh node for you! You can order in Buffalo, NY or Phoenix, AZ. You're choice!

Each and every VPS that we provide comes with the ability to set RDNS from with in the VPS Control Panel. Each account is also provided Free Domain DNS hosting.

Features:&lt;br&gt;
CPU: 2 Core&lt;br&gt;
RAM: 1GB&lt;br&gt;
VSWAP: 2GB&lt;br&gt;
DISKSPACE: 100GB&lt;br&gt;
BANDWIDTH: 1TB&lt;br&gt;
IP Addresses: 1 (IPv4)&lt;br&gt;
Price: $5.99/month&lt;br&gt;
Port: 100MBPS&lt;br&gt;
Order [Here](https://core.xfusesolutions.com/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=40) _(Location can be picked on the order form.)_

Our VPS nodes are hooked to a 1GBPS connection and features RAID10 protection.
More IP's available upon request at a rate currently set at $1.50/month per IP.

